## Optional starter you can fill now

* `<<USE_CASES>>`: e.g., ‚ÄúProtect LLM completion API calls to `provider_X` from cascading failures/timeouts; fallback to cached answer or graceful message.‚Äù
* Threshold sketch: ‚ÄúOpen on ‚â•50% error rate over last 20 requests or ‚â•5 consecutive failures; half-open after 30s with 3 probes; close on 3/3 success.‚Äù

