>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>

Got it ‚Äî let‚Äôs break this down systematically.

You‚Äôre writing a **zero-shot instruction prompt** whose goal is:
‚û°Ô∏è Guide the most capable AI agent to deeply analyze the internal Python library `ent_pycore`, understand its functions, and propose logic/designs that can be built using it.

---

## üîé Analysis of Your Current Prompt

**Your version:**

> Pip install ent_pycore.
> We have ent_pycore inbuilt library in our org, and I want to analyse all the functions in the library ent_pycore and help me to achieve this technically and see what all logic is possible with the internaly python library.
